snippet.textDisplay: I was trained by my mother- finish your plate... even if I was full.. as an adult I really think its why I'm overweight. I can hear my head saying " finish your plate" even when I'm full because I spent too much money and I don't want to waste it or whatever. We have to learn its okay to say no and stop. I don't make my kids finish their plates now. When they are full, they can leave the table. I don't want to force them to eat and get them in the mindset as teens and adults they have to eat the whole plate because they made too much or spent too much money on it, when the belly is Full its full.
